This repositories contains source code for implementing a captcha system:

- Full ajaxified;
- Using jQuery plugin named sexy-captcha;
- With simple java servlet and JSPs;
- With JSTL;

All the information about this project, are available on my blog:
[coming soon..]

The plugin of jQuery used is available on the author's page:
http://blog.lukeblackamore.com/2009/10/sexy-captcha-new-drag-and-drop-captcha.html
